SELECT Q1.WORKER_ID, Q1. WORKER_NAME, Q1.EMAIL, Q1.CURRENT_POSITION_NM, Q1.BUSINESS_UNIT_DESCRIPTION, Q1.ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME, Q1.LOCATION_DESCRIPTION, Q1.COMPANY_DESCRIPTION, Q1.CODE_OF_CONDUCT_MAIN_ID, Q1.REPORTS_TO_EID , Q2.REPORTS_TO_NAME, Q2.REPORTS_TO_EMAIL, Q2.REPORTS_TO_CURR_POS_NM, Q2.REPORTS_TO_ORG_UNIT_NM, Q1.ROOT_ID, Q1.ROOT_NAME, CASE WHEN (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'EVP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%EXEC%VP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SVP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SR%VP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%PRESIDENT%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%VICE%PRESIDENT%') then 'ABOVE VP' WHEN ((upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%VP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%EVP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%EXEC%VP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%SVP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%SR%VP%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SITE%PRESIDENT%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'VICE%') ) then 'VP' ELSE NULL END as POSITION_FLAG FROM (SELECT lower(WORKER_ID) as WORKER_ID, WORKER_FIRST_NM||', '||WORKER_LAST_NM as REPORTS_TO_NAME, INTERNET_EMAIL_AD as REPORTS_TO_EMAIL, CURRENT_POSITION_NM as REPORTS_TO_CURR_POS_NM, ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME as REPORTS_TO_ORG_UNIT_NM FROM SAP.D_WORKER_ALL WHERE SCD_IS_CURRENT_YN = 'Y' and CURRENT_STATUS_CD in (1,5) )Q2, (SELECT lower(WORKER_ID) as WORKER_ID, lower(REPORTS_TO_EID) as REPORTS_TO_EID , EMAIL, WORKER_NAME, CURRENT_POSITION_NM, BUSINESS_UNIT_DESCRIPTION, ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME, LOCATION_DESCRIPTION, COMPANY_DESCRIPTION, CODE_OF_CONDUCT_MAIN_ID, CONNECT_BY_ROOT WORKER_ID as ROOT_ID, CONNECT_BY_ROOT WORKER_NAME as ROOT_NAME FROM ( SELECT WORKER_ID, REPORTS_TO_EID, WORKER_FIRST_NM||', '||WORKER_LAST_NM as WORKER_NAME, INTERNET_EMAIL_AD as EMAIL, CURRENT_POSITION_NM, BUSINESS_UNIT_DESCRIPTION, ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME, LOCATION_DESCRIPTION, COMPANY_DESCRIPTION, CODE_OF_CONDUCT_MAIN_ID FROM SAP.D_WORKER_ALL WHERE SCD_IS_CURRENT_YN = 'Y' and CURRENT_STATUS_CD in (1,5) ) CONNECT BY NOCYCLE PRIOR lower(WORKER_ID) = lower(REPORTS_TO_EID) START WITH lower(WORKER_ID) = lower( #prompt('pLEADEREID','string' )#) )Q1 WHERE Q1.REPORTS_TO_EID = Q2.WORKER_ID

SELECT Q1.ENTERPRISE_ID, Q1. WORKER_NAME, Q1.INTERNET_EMAIL_AD, Q1.CURRENT_POSITION_NM, Q1.COMPANY_DESCRIPTION, Q1.LOCATION_DESCRIPTION, Q1.ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME, Q1.Reports_to_EID, Q2.REPORTS_TO_NAME, Q1.current_Business_category, Q1.worker_type_cd, CASE WHEN (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'EVP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%EXEC%VP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SVP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SR%VP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SR%VP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SEN%PRESIDENT%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%PRESIDENT%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%VICE%PRESIDENT%') then 'ABOVE VP' WHEN ((upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%VP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%EVP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%EXEC%VP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%SVP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%SR%VP%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SITE%PRESIDENT%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'VICE%') ) then 'VP LEVEL' ELSE NULL END as POSITION_FLAG FROM (select lower(ENTERPRISE_ID) AS ENTERPRISE_ID, WORKER_FIRST_NM||' '||WORKER_LAST_NM as WORKER_NAME, INTERNET_EMAIL_AD, CURRENT_POSITION_NM, COMPANY_DESCRIPTION, LOCATION_DESCRIPTION, ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME, lower(Reports_to_EID) AS Reports_to_EID, current_Business_category, worker_type_cd from sap.d_worker_all where SCD_IS_CURRENT_YN = 'Y' and CURRENT_STATUS_CD in (1,5) and WORKER_TYPE_CD = 'E' and lower(ENTERPRISE_ID) not in ('thoma35','robe930' ) and /* As per new req 08/10/2020, exclude VP above positions */ ( upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'EVP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%EXEC%VP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SVP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SR%VP%' or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%PRESIDENT%' ) or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SITE%PRESIDENT%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'VICE%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'VP%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%VP%') ) )Q1, (select lower(ENTERPRISE_ID) AS ENTERPRISE_ID, WORKER_FIRST_NM||' '||WORKER_LAST_NM as REPORTS_TO_NAME from sap.d_worker_all where SCD_IS_CURRENT_YN = 'Y' and CURRENT_STATUS_CD in (1,5) )Q2 where Q1.Reports_to_EID = Q2.ENTERPRISE_ID(+)

querySubject.name: VP_LIST
querySubject.description: Query is using the D_WORKER_ALL. CURRENT_POSITION_NM filtered for VP, SITE VICE PRESIDENT and VICE PRESIDENT's and WORKER_TP_CD = 'E'

dbQuery.sql: SELECT Q1.ENTERPRISE_ID, Q1. WORKER_NAME, Q1.INTERNET_EMAIL_AD, Q1.CURRENT_POSITION_NM, Q1.COMPANY_DESCRIPTION, Q1.LOCATION_DESCRIPTION, Q1.ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME, Q1.Reports_to_EID, Q2.REPORTS_TO_NAME, Q1.current_Business_category, Q1.worker_type_cd, CASE WHEN (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%VP%' or upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%VICE%') then 'VP' ELSE NULL END as POSITION_FLAG FROM (select lower(ENTERPRISE_ID) AS ENTERPRISE_ID, WORKER_FIRST_NM||' '||WORKER_LAST_NM as WORKER_NAME, INTERNET_EMAIL_AD, CURRENT_POSITION_NM, COMPANY_DESCRIPTION, LOCATION_DESCRIPTION, ORGANIZATION_UNIT_NAME, lower(Reports_to_EID) AS Reports_to_EID, current_Business_category, worker_type_cd from sap.d_worker_all where SCD_IS_CURRENT_YN = 'Y' and CURRENT_STATUS_CD in (1,5) and WORKER_TYPE_CD = 'E' and lower(ENTERPRISE_ID) not in ('thoma35','robe930' ) and /* This filter will get all VP or VICE PRESIDENT or SITE VICE PRESIDENT*/ ( (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like '%VP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%EVP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%EXEC%VP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%SVP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like '%SR%VP%' and upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) not like 'SEN%VICE%' ) or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'SITE%PRESIDENT%') or (upper(CURRENT_POSITION_NM) like 'VICE%') ) )Q1, (select lower(ENTERPRISE_ID) AS ENTERPRISE_ID, WORKER_FIRST_NM||' '||WORKER_LAST_NM as REPORTS_TO_NAME from sap.d_worker_all where SCD_IS_CURRENT_YN = 'Y' and CURRENT_STATUS_CD in (1,5) )Q2 where Q1.Reports_to_EID = Q2.ENTERPRISE_ID

select PH.RECIPIENT_GROUP, PH.FAILURE_YN, PH.ENTERPRISE_ID, DW.WORKER_FIRST_NM, DW.WORKER_LAST_NM, DW.INTERNET_EMAIL_AD, DW.CURRENT_POSITION_NM, PH.LOCATION, PH.DEPARTMENT, PH.COMPANY, PS.DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN, PS.SENDER_EMAIL FROM SAP.D_WORKER_ALL DW, CDM.F_PHISHING_SIMULATION PH, CDM.D_PHISHING_SIMULATIONS PS where lower(DW.ENTERPRISE_ID) = lower(PH.ENTERPRISE_ID) and PH.RECIPIENT_GROUP = PS.RECIPIENT_GROUP and DW.SCD_IS_CURRENT_YN = 'Y' and DW.CURRENT_STATUS_CD in (1,5) and (PH.FAILURE_YN in ('TRUE','Yes') ) Order by RECIPIENT_GROUP Desc

SELECT A.RECIPIENT_GROUP as RECPT_GROUP, A.DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN as CAMPIGN_DATE, A.DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG as DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG FROM (SELECT RECIPIENT_GROUP, DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN,DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG FROM CDM.D_PHISHING_SIMULATIONS ) A, (SELECT MAX(DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN) AS "END_DATE" FROM ( SELECT DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN FROM CDM.D_PHISHING_SIMULATIONS where ( 'BAJIBA1' in (#CSVIdentityNameList()# ) or 'PARAG01' in (#CSVIdentityNameList()#) or 'Web_MossItrmSecPolicyPhish_6M' in (#CSVIdentityNameList()#) or DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG = 'Y' ) ) )B WHERE to_char(A.DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN, 'YYYYMM') = to_char(B."END_DATE", 'YYYYMM')

SELECT A.RECIPIENT_GROUP AS RECPT_GROUP, A.DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN AS CAMPIGN_DATE, A.DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG as DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG FROM (SELECT RECIPIENT_GROUP, DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN, DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG FROM CDM.D_PHISHING_SIMULATIONS ) A, (SELECT TRUNC(ADD_MONTHS(MAX(DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN),-11),'month') AS "BEGIN_DATE", LAST_DAY(MAX(DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN))AS "END_DATE" FROM CDM.D_PHISHING_SIMULATIONS )B WHERE A.DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN BETWEEN B."BEGIN_DATE" AND B."END_DATE" /* The below condition pulls Recipient Groups from current year, if you want to enable Rolling 12 Months logic, just disable this condition */ --and extract(Year from A.DATE_OF_CAMPAIGN) = extract(Year from CURRENT_DATE)

filterDefinition.expression: 'BAJIBA1' in (#CSVIdentityNameList()# ) or 'PARAG01' in (#CSVIdentityNameList()#) or 'Web_MossItrmSecPolicyPhish_6M' in (#CSVIdentityNameList()#) or [Database Layer].[PHISHING_R12_CAMPAIGNS].[DATA_VALIDATION_FLAG] = 'Y'
